Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神獸鏡的光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說我們有弒神的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對面就是Symphogear殺手Death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然真有效唉
