Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:17.72,IN_F_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&\an2}Gatrandis babel ziggurat edenal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:28.16,IN_F_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&\an2}Emustolronzen fine el zizzl
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高能量反應自地核開始蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認世界樹開始崩解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界各地亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去Gear…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要挺不住Death
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(616,671.666)}Shem-ha
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦誠與孤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何故拒絕融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因我們不能簡單地互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能夠珍視他人　相親相愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論誰也不能奪走這份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縱因此至未來仍有互相傷害痛苦不堪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在互相傷害的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也並未停止腳下的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以超越神明知慧的光芒創造著歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善盡汝等使命便是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}未來皆在汝等手中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧　響
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神名她…用那巨大的雙手保護了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs28\pos(361.333,672.999)}Shem-ha
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　這就是大家攜手共創的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八千八聲　杜鵑啼血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要仍然身為人類
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就很難即相連相通又不互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在這由隔閡而生的焦灼中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.43,0:23:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孕育了無數可貴的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說　響
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.23,0:23:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我一直有話想親口對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我想說的和未來一樣就好了
